{"tid":2145661,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊明獲保釋出院透露現況　樂易玲述事件起因：當時他可能因壓力過大、疲勞或其他狀況","createTime":"2020-08-08T07:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T07:37:23.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d00f0ddd7c16cc333d9f9c44b08afea89a7a4c66","tid":2145661,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"楊明在約凌晨零時份疑酒後駕車失事，他駕駛的私家車沿馬己仙峽道落山，途至近玫瑰別墅對開一個左彎位時，突然失控撞向防撞欄後再衝前，撞毀一個交通指示牌，右邊車頭鏟上石壆後停下。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，楊明當時滿身酒氣，行出汽車後腳步不穩，他自稱不適由警員扶上救護車，但拒絕俗稱「吹波波」的酒精呼氣測試被捕，以及被送往瑪麗醫院。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指他已經保釋，並已離開醫院。他回應傳媒現時身體狀況只簡單表示：「冇事。」沒有進一步回應。<br />\n<br />\n至於無綫電視助理總經理（藝員管理及發展）樂易玲，回應傳媒查詢稱：<br />\n&quot;據初步了解楊明昨晚駕車回家時發生意外，受了輕傷，幸好沒有涉及其他人。<br />\n當時他可能因壓力過大、疲勞或其他狀況，汽車失控撞向路旁防撞欄和石壆，車頭毀爛。<br />\n事後他被送往醫院，經治療後已出院。<br />\n現時希望給予他時間休息，盡早痊愈。<br />\n公司會進一步了解事情和向楊明提供所需的協助。&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2715000/2718865/MatYeungthumb02_20200808_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2715000%2F2718865%2FMatYeungthumb02_20200808_S_1024.jpg&h=299982d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0465789840f861ecad3104e0ef1e02467038aca","tid":2145661,"uid":56819,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:08:17.000Z","msg":"壓力大就可以醉駕,唔使罰?"},{"pid":"0bcfdea9b0e2ac9811339f9bda4e4a9f5c509d20","tid":2145661,"uid":300630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:09:57.000Z","msg":"坐牢未？"},{"pid":"0895427640825a348f611f0107fc824664155b72","tid":2145661,"uid":242036,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:12:01.000Z","msg":"一個 &quot;酒&quot; 字都冇提過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a85aa6e46611e93361fa7b05fbbc9ceddab05ae","tid":2145661,"uid":126898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"楊明幾時叫樂易玲收嗲 犯法就係犯法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad534c402d80da96e3323bc9f108917b1ce8029","tid":2145661,"uid":282310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:17:13.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;...或其他狀況&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n咁同冇講有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da5c4ed4007be5f923f944d7e81786ab18cdee43","tid":2145661,"uid":22796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:20:00.000Z","msg":"即係壓力過大就可以醉駕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0958bc9c69a792204c0ad2b472e27e95cb515ba0","tid":2145661,"uid":11454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:22:27.000Z","msg":"果然係黑警劇第一男主角<br />\n方法演技，入形入格<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0e2c7111f6cd2408414ac1dd42ab28e5cb0074","tid":2145661,"uid":39010,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"真係好醉駕完咩事都無<br />\n又唔洗做呼氣 <br />\n藍c 偽人係唔同d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e54f6acb0841c4ed12ea2f16c451d4591a07ea","tid":2145661,"uid":9013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"原來壓力大可以生產酒精"},{"pid":"f1b8a8c6cde8e0555c82472c1d2f94c0a8390429","tid":2145661,"uid":162674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:26:54.000Z","msg":"壓力大可唔可以強姦樂小姐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe6f58bc6af64a4f3c6db318c50cd2da1be6f7","tid":2145661,"uid":267880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔吹波仔都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下期訓練班幾時開 想入"},{"pid":"bff4bed4eb74dbc5dfe9bcf375b3d330014fa817","tid":2145661,"uid":192409,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:28:03.000Z","msg":